; GPGL Command File
; Description: Test draw - 10mm square using pen (Tool 2) with pressure
; Position: (10mm, 10mm) from origin

; Setup
FN0
SO0
J2
!10,2
FX5,2
FC18,2
FE0,0

; Move to start (pen up)
M200,200

; Pen down explicitly
SP1

; Draw 10mm x 10mm square
D200,400
D400,400
D400,200
D200,200

; Pen up
SP0

; Return home
H
